Subject: drm/edid: pass a timing pointer to is_detailed_timing_descriptor()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: a9b1f15f53313f967edd5088a60970cc829ab5a6
